data.description: Open House Saturday 11am-1pm.  This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath ranch is the perfect retreat. With a fenced backyard, shed, and screened porch, you'll relish outdoor living. Inside, hardwood floors, coved ceilings, and a cozy family room with a fireplace await. Ample closets, an ensuite primary bedroom, and a 2-car garage make daily life a breeze.  Don't miss out on this opportunity for comfort and convenience!
